Dialogue: 1,0:24:51.45,0:24:59.77,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0\c&HDFDFDF&\pos(321.556,287.319)}Non perdetevi il prossimo episodio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.55,0:24:55.68,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,... con i giovani detective in prima linea!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.68,0:24:56.77,Default - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Di nuovo?!
